sources.description:
Gavin Ransom sets out to make millions by blanketing the hills of northern California with flamboyant, mini mansions. His sister Olive a raving environmentalist, thinks otherwise.  Caught between Olive's righteousness and Gavin's affection, the idealistic and innocent Zoe, must choose between a cause she's grown up supporting, or the affections of a man who stands for everything she believes is wrong.

Directed by Jonathan Parker
2005
Starring Noah Wyle, Illeana Douglas, Kate Mara
